    (:~ Get Mentions of Entities in a Document: /doc/{docId}/mentions.rdf 
    @param $docId ID of the Document
    @returns RDF of Mentions of Entites in a Document
    :)
    
    (:Example Response:)
    (:
    <rdf:RDF xmlns:rdf="http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#"
